parameters: Michio: "How long are you gonna make me wait?! Hurry up, will ya!"

Michio: "Hey, aren't you done yet? I've been waiting for like 30
minutes!"

Masahito: "They say the membership fee is free as a grand opening
celebration. That's awesome!"
Katsuya: "I'm gonna get ripped and capture Minami-chan's heart!"

Daichi: "That bastard Takumi... cutting in line like that! Next time I
see him, I'm gonna knock his lights out!"
Staff: "Ah, no, it's nothing. Excuse me!"
Yui: "Excuse me... Is this the Muscle Gym that was advertised on TV?"

Clerk: "You saw our commercial and decided to come. Thank you very
much!"

Clerk: "We are currently running an opening celebration campaign. If
you sign up now, you can use the facilities for free for one week."

Clerk: "After the free period ends, if you continue to use our
facilities, there will be a monthly usage fee of 5,000 yen."
Clerk: "Would you like to sign up?"
Clerk: "Your name is Yui Morisaki. One female member, correct?"

Clerk: "For men, please head to the facility on the right-hand side...
For women, please proceed down the left-hand corridor and take the
elevator to the fourth floor."
Yui: "The fourth floor, got it. Thank you!"

Yui: "(No way... I don't have time to deal with him. Just pretend not
to notice. Pretend not to notice.)"
Takumi: "Why are you ignoring me? Can't you hear me?"
Yui: "Yes, yes. I can hear you just fine!"
Takumi: "What a coincidence to meet here. What are you doing here?"
Yui: "More importantly, why are you here?"
Takumi: "Me? I was thinking of getting in some training."

Takumi: "Next week, there's a big pool opening in the Forus district.
You know about it, right?"
Yui: "(Could it be that he's also going to that pool?)"
Yui: "Ah, is that so... I had no idea."

Takumi: "I was thinking of inviting you to that pool! I'd be disliked
if I had a sloppy body, right?"

Yui: "(Instead of training your body, you should work on fixing your
arrogance and bad habits with women.)"

Yui: "(But training to invite me to the pool... He's serious about
this sort of thing.)"

Yui: "Well... I've put on a little weight recently. I'm here more for
dieting than training."
Takumi: "Huh, you've gained weight? I can't tell at all."

Takumi: "You're cute just the way you are, no need to push yourself
too hard."

Takumi: "You really gave it to me the other day... about making Azami-
chan cry."

Takumi: "I've been seriously reflecting on your words... You were
absolutely right."

Takumi: "From now on, I'm going to change my ways and train both my
mind and body. I want to be as cool as that Pony Celes!"
Takumi: "Let's both do our best then!"

Yui: "(He wants to be as cool as Pony Celes. Hmm, maybe he has
reflected a little bit...)"

Takumi: "(The reason I'm training my body is to rape you with brute
force. Just in case I can't bring you down.)"

Takumi: "(Actually, inviting Morisaki to the pool isn't a bad idea at
all. It seems like she believed the lie I blurted out on the spot...)"

Takumi: "(Wait for me, Morisaki. You're definitely going to be
embraced by me!)"
Polka: "I sense a tremendous power coming from ahead."

Polka: "It's a terrifying force, on par with the executives of
Zaidarg-G."

Pony-Celes: "Honestly, you worry too much. No matter how strong the
opponent is, I won't lose to the likes of Zaidarg-G."

Polka: "Don't underestimate Zaidarg-G. Courage and recklessness are not
the same thing!"
Pony-Celes: "That's true, but... then what should we do?"

Polka: "There must be a reason why a mere monster, not even an
executive, has gained such immense power."
Polka: "Take a look around. There might be a secret hidden somewhere."

Polka: "Yui-chan, I'll say it again... Don't recklessly charge in,
it's absolutely not okay."
Pony-Celes: "I get it. I'm not that foolish, you know."

Staff: "Excuse me, could you please not talk to me right now? I'm in
the middle of putting away something \C[17]important\C[0]..."
【\i[291]Key of the Azure Star】has been obtained!
